item.dc:creator: @jc22493 Jc22493
item.description:
@jc22493 wrote:

[quote=“nemoigescape, post:8, topic:280920”]so you wanted to be spoon fed the whole thing, by copying that what exactly did you learn :S?

you didnt learn anything, if you try a little harder to do things your self you will know how to do stuff yourself in future, which is a lot more rewarding :)[/quote]
I wouldn’t say this is ultimately spoon-feeding, since no member would want to find all the safezone coordinates of RuneScape, (although he could have created a method that indicated when a player was in the wild, rather than out of the wild.).

But, I do agree with your opinion; doing things yourself is much more rewarding, and you can obtain knowledge by doing so.
